## Next steps

You can now fit a Cox model, read hazard ratios, and assess overall fit.

- [Cox model diagnostics](cox-diagnostics.qmd) checks the proportional hazards assumption,
computes residuals, predicts survival curves, and adds robust variance and stratification.
- [Parametric survival models](parametric-models.qmd) offers an alternative modeling approach
